Prepare custom functions

case_control_microbiome <- function(d.meta, md.meta, target_disease){
  e <- c()
  error <- c()  
  p <- c()
  fc <- c()
  
  p_adj <- c()
  e_adj <- c()  
  error_adj <- c()  
  
  p_adj_l <- c()
  e_adj_l <- c()
  error_adj_l <- c()
  
  rel <- c()
  rel2 <- c()
  rel_without <- c()  
  
  for(i in 1:ncol(d.meta)){

    if(grepl("Shannon", colnames(d.meta)[i])){
      d.meta[, i] <- 10 ^ d.meta[, i]
    }
    
    d.min <- min(d.meta[d.meta != 0])/2
    if(length(unique(md.meta$study)) == 1){
      res <- glm(log10(d.meta[, i] + d.min) ~ md.meta$disease)
      m <- glm(log10(d.meta[, i] + d.min) ~ md.meta$disease + md.meta$count)
    }else{
      res <- glm(log10(d.meta[, i] + d.min) ~ md.meta$disease + md.meta$study)
      m <- glm(log10(d.meta[, i] + d.min) ~ md.meta$disease + md.meta$count + md.meta$study)
    }
    
    p[i] <- summary(res)$coefficients[2, 4]
    e[i] <- summary(res)$coefficients[2, 1]
    error[i] <- summary(res)$coefficients[2, 2]    

    p_adj[i] <- summary(m)$coefficients[2, 4]
    e_adj[i] <- summary(m)$coefficients[2, 1] 
    error_adj[i] <- summary(m)$coefficients[2, 2]     
    
    cont <- d.meta[md.meta$disease == "Control", i] %>% mean()
    case <- d.meta[md.meta$disease != "Control", i] %>% mean()
  }
  
  num <- table(md.meta$disease)
  fdr <- p.adjust(p, method = "fdr")
  fdr_adj <- p.adjust(p_adj, method = "fdr")
  
  df <- data.frame(name = colnames(d.meta), 
                   p = p, fdr = fdr, e = e, error = error, 
                   p_adj = p_adj, e_adj = e_adj, error_adj = error_adj, fdr_adj = fdr_adj, 
                   disease = target_disease, case_n = num[2], cont_n = num[1])
  
  df$name <- df$name %>% str_replace("ref_mOTU_v25_", "") %>% str_replace("meta_mOTU_v25_", "")
  
  return(df)
}

## function for microbial load
case_control_count <- function(md.meta, target_disease){
  e <- c()
  error <- c()
  p <- c()
    
  if(length(unique(md.meta$study)) == 1){
    res <- glm(md.meta$count ~ md.meta$disease)
  }else{
    res <- glm(md.meta$count ~ md.meta$disease + md.meta$study)
  }
  p <- summary(res)$coefficients[2, 4]
  e <- summary(res)$coefficients[2, 1]
  error[i] <- summary(res)$coefficients[2, 2]  
  
  num <- table(md.meta$disease)
  temp <- tapply(md.meta$count, md.meta$disease, median)
  
  df <- data.frame(name = "count", p = p, e = e, error = error, disease = target_disease, case_n = num[2], cont_n = num[1])
  df <- df %>% mutate(case_med = 10 ^ temp[2]) %>% mutate(cont_med = 10 ^ temp[1])  

  return(df)
}

Disease meta-analysis

files <- list.files("out/disease_each/", pattern = "d.rmp.rds$") %>% paste0("out/disease_each/", .)
i <- files[4]
i
## [1] "out/disease_each/C.difficile infection.d.rmp.rds"
for(i in files){
  print(i)
  d.meta <- read_rds(i)
  md.meta <- i %>% str_replace("d.rmp.rds", "md.rds") %>% read_rds()
  target_disease <- i %>% str_remove(".*\\/") %>% str_remove("\\.d.rmp.*")
  
  ## remove minor species
  keep <- apply(d.meta, 2, mean) > 1E-4 & apply(d.meta > 0, 2, mean) > 0.05
  d.meta <- d.meta[, keep]
  d.meta <- d.meta %>% select(-contains("-1"))
  
  ## case-control comparison using all the samples
  md.meta$disease <- factor(md.meta$disease, levels = c("Control", target_disease))
  
  ## for microbiome (RMP)
  res <- case_control_microbiome(d.meta, md.meta, target_disease)

  ## for microbiome (QMP)
  d.meta2 <- d.meta %>% select(-contains("Shannon"))
  q.meta <- d.meta2 * (10 ^ md.meta$count)  
  res.q <- case_control_microbiome(q.meta, md.meta, target_disease)

  ## for predicted microbial loads
  res.count <- case_control_count(md.meta, target_disease)  

  out <- paste0("out/disease_each/", target_disease, ".res.rmp.rds")
  saveRDS(res, file = out)
  
  out <- paste0("out/disease_each/", target_disease, ".res.qmp.rds")
  saveRDS(res.q, file = out)
  
  out <- paste0("out/disease_each/", target_disease, ".count.rds")
  saveRDS(res.count, file = out)
  
  out <- paste0("out/disease_each/", target_disease, ".md.rds")
  md.meta$group <- ifelse(md.meta$disease == "Control", "Control", "Case")
  md.meta$disease_label <- target_disease
  saveRDS(md.meta, file = out)
}

res$facet <- ifelse(rownames(res) == "Crohn's disease", "Crohn's disease", ifelse(rownames(res) == "Ulcerative colitis", "Ulcerative colitis", ""))

files <- list.files("out/disease_each/", pattern = "res.rmp.rds") %>% paste0("out/disease_each/", .)

res <- c()

## prepare df
table <- res %>% select(name, e, disease) %>% spread(disease, e)
rownames(table) <- table$name
table <- table[, -1]  

## exclude species with too many NAs
keep <- apply(is.na(table), 1, sum) < 5
table <- table[keep, ]

## detect discriminating species using wilcoxon rank-sum test
p <- c()
e <- c()
na.sum <- c()

i <- 1
for(i in 1:nrow(table)){
  na.sum[i] <-   table[i, ] %>% is.na() %>% sum()  
  p[i] <- wilcox.test(as.numeric(table[i, ]) ~ factor(stat$dir))$p.value
}

df <- data.frame(name = rownames(table), p = p, fdr = p.adjust(p, method = "fdr"), na = na.sum) %>% arrange(p)
df <- df %>% filter(name != "-1")

df.sig <- df %>% filter(na == 0) %>% filter(fdr < 0.05) %>% arrange(fdr) %>% head(n = 30)

sp_ord <- df.sig$name
keep <- rownames(table) %in% df.sig$name
table <- table[keep, ]

df.old <- df
df <- table %>% t() %>% data.frame(check.names = F) %>% 
  mutate(e = stat$e) %>% rownames_to_column() %>% gather("key", "value", -rowname, -e)

keep <- res$name %in% rownames(table)
res2 <- res[keep, ]

df <- inner_join(res2,  stat[, c("disease", "e")], by = "disease")
df <- left_join(df, df.old[, c("name", "fdr")], by = "name")

df$ast <- ifelse(df$fdr.x < 0.01, "**", ifelse(df$fdr.x < 0.1, "*", ""))
df$dir <- ifelse(df$e.y > 0, "positive", "negative")
df$class <- ifelse(grepl("Shannon", df$name), "diversity", "sp")

## prepare df for NAs
df.na <- complete(df, name, disease)
df.na$class <- "sp"
df.na <- df.na[is.na(df.na$p), ]

df.dir.uniq <- df %>% select(disease, dir) %>% unique()

temp <- left_join(df.na[, "disease"], df.dir.uniq)
## Joining with `by = join_by(disease)`
df.na$dir <- temp$dir

df$name <- factor(df$name, levels = sp_ord)
